\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Biology\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Biology\\\">Biology<\\/a>\\u00a0is the science concerned with the study of life.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"Definition\\\"><\\/span>There is currently no consensus regarding the definition of life. One popular definition is that\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Organism\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Organism\\\">organisms<\\/a>\\u00a0are\\u00a0<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" title=\\\"Open system (thermodynamics)\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Open_system_(thermodynamics)\\\">open systems<\\/a>\\u00a0that maintain\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Homeostasis\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Homeostasis\\\">homeostasis<\\/a>, are composed of\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Cell (biology)\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Cell_(biology)\\\">cells<\\/a>, have a\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Biological life cycle\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Biological_life_cycle\\\">life cycle<\\/a>, undergo\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Metabolism\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Metabolism\\\">metabolism<\\/a>, can\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Cell growth\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Cell_growth\\\">grow<\\/a>,\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Adaptation\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Adaptation\\\">adapt<\\/a>\\u00a0to their environment, respond to\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Stimulus (physiology)\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Stimulus_(physiology)\\\">stimuli<\\/a>,\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Reproduction\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Reproduction\\\">reproduce<\\/a>\\u00a0and\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Evolution\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Evolution\\\">evolve<\\/a>. Other definitions sometimes include non-cellular life forms such as\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Virus\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Virus\\\">viruses<\\/a>\\u00a0and\\u00a0<a title=\\\"Viroid\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Viroid\\\">viroids<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"eael_dch_container_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"-3\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"-20\",\"left\":\"-1\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"16\",\"right\":\"16\",\"bottom\":\"16\",\"left\":\"16\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"eael-dual-color-header\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
